                        <condition key="good">Many fols. are stained with wax, dirt and water.&#xD;
Traces of a previous overback are preserved on the inner side of the front board.&#xD;
The leather cover is damaged, partly missing (on the spine and boards).&#xD;
The Ms. has been resewn.&#xD;
Fols. 13, 14, 15 are missplaced (e.g., fol. 12vb should have been followed by fol. 16ra).&#xD;
Fols. 12, 66, 67, 104 are mutilated.&#xD;
Fols. 92, 95 are of a smaller size.&#xD;
