                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 15rb: Supplication for the commissioners and the scribe.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 15rb: ኦአኃውየ፡ ደቂቀ፡ ዛቲ፡ መቅደስ፡ ኢትርስኡነ፡ በጊዜ፡ አንበብክምዋ፡ ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ለአግብርቲክሙ፡ ተስፋ፡ ጽዮን፡ መርደ፡ ክዮስ፡ ግደ፡ ማርያም፡ ወለጸሐፊሐ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ዘድንግል፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 112rb: Ownership note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 112rb: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ፍትሐት፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ዘአጋምዮ፡ ዘሠረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ወዘተአገላ፡ ወዘአልሃላ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በቃለ፡ ፫፻፲ወ፰ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ወፈድፋደ፡ ይኩን፡ መክፈልቱ፡ ምስለ፡ አርዮስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Pen trials: fols. 1v, 2r. &#xD;
- Minor notes in the margins: fols. 1v, 25v.&#xD;
- Words እገሌ and እገሊት, "so-and-so" are marked by thin lines above and below throughout the Ms.&#xD;
- Space for rubricated names left unfilled: fols. 9va, 10ra, 10va, 12vb, 18va, 35v, 44ra, 46ra, 50va, 51ra, 73va, 107rb.&#xD;
- Corrections written interlineally: fols. 28rb, 42va, 43va, 44vb, 74vb, 84va, 86va, 92ra, 97vb, 113rb.&#xD;
- Immediate correction marked by thin lines above and below words: fols. 35r, 103va.&#xD;
- The scribe used compressed script in fols. 112va-116vb.</item>
                     </list>
